high_descs: Move to the right of toilet turn right towards bath tub.
Pick up dispenser from the bath tub.
Turn around towards toilet.
Place dispenser on top of the toilet.
Move to the left side sink closet to the wall.
Open sink cabinet and pick up dispenser from out of the cabinet and close the door.
Move to the right of toilet and turn towards the toilet.
Place dispenser on top of toilet next to the other one.
anns.task_desc: Place two dispensers on top of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn to your right and move to the tub.
Pick up the bottle that is on the ledge of the tub.
Turn around and move to the toilet.
Place the bottle on the back of the toilet.
Turn to the left and go to the sink.
Open the cabinet door on the far left  under the sink. Grab the bottle.
Turn left and go to the toilet.
Place the bottle on the far left on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move bottles to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the left side of the tub.
Pick up the bottle of lotion that is resting on the edge of the tub.
Turn around to face the toilet.
Place the bottle of lotion on the top of the toilet tank in the middle.
Turn left and walk over to the leftmost sink.
Open the leftmost cabinet door below the sink and take out the bottle of lotion, then close the cabinet door.
Turn right and walk back over to the tub, then turn left ad walk up to the towel rack, then turn left again to face the toilet.
Place the bottle of lotion on the far edge of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles of lotion to the top of the toilet tank.
